from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score
from sklearn.metrics import calinski_harabasz_score

silh_score=[]
cali_score=[]
inertia_score=[]

def new_func(kmeans):
    return kmeans.inertia_

for i in range(2,7):
    kmeans=KMeans(n_clusters=i,random_state=123).fit(pca_trans)
    score=silhouette_score(data_a,kmeans.labels_)
    silh_score.append(score)
    score=calinski_harabasz_score(data_a,kmeans.labels_)
    cali_score.append(score)
    score=new_func(kmeans)
    inertia_score.append(score)

print('',silh_score)
print('calinski_harabasz',cali_score)
print('inertia',inertia_score)  #inertia

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.plot(range(2,7),silh_score,'b*--',linewidth=1,markersize=10,label='silhouette_score')
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('cluster')
plt.ylabel('score')
plt.show()

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.plot(range(2,7),cali_score,'rs--',linewidth=1,markersize=10,label='calinski_harabasz_score')
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('cluster')
plt.ylabel('score')
plt.show()

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))
plt.plot(range(2,7),inertia_score,'go--',linewidth=1,markersize=10,label='inertia_score')
plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('cluster')
plt.ylabel('score')
plt.show()

建立高钾DBSCAN聚类模型、评价聚类模型选择最优聚类簇数目¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.cluster import DBSCAN

for i in np.arange(6.8,9,0.3):
    for j in np.arange(2,4):
        DB=DBSCAN(eps=i,min_samples=j).fit(pca_trans)
        labels=DB.labels_
        n_clusters_=len(set(labels))-(1 if -1 in labels else 0)
        n_noise_=labels.tolist().count(-1)
        if n_clusters_ <= 5 and n_noise_ <= 5:
            print("eps={},min_samples={}".format(i,j))
            print("{},{}".format(n_clusters_,n_noise_))
            print("",labels)
            silh_score=silhouette_score(pca_trans,DB.labels_)
            cali_score=calinski_harabasz_score(pca_trans,DB.labels_)          
            print("silhouette{}".format(silh_score))
            print("calinski_harabasz{}".format(cali_score))
            print("\n---------------------------------------\n")

from sklearn.cluster import KMeans
from sklearn.metrics import silhouette_score
from sklearn.metrics import calinski_harabasz_score

silh_score=[]
cali_score=[]
inertia_score=[]

for i in range(2,7):
    kmeans=KMeans(n_clusters=i,random_state=123).fit(pca_trans)
    score=silhouette_score(data_b,kmeans.labels_)
    silh_score.append(score)
    score=calinski_harabasz_score(data_b,kmeans.labels_)
    cali_score.append(score)
    score=kmeans.inertia_
    inertia_score.append(score)

print('',silh_score)
print('calinski_harabasz',cali_score)
print('inertia',inertia_score)  #inertia

plt.figure(figsize=(6,4))

plt.show()

plt.legend()
plt.xlabel('cluster')
plt.ylabel('score')
plt.show()

建立铅钡DBSCAN聚类模型、评价聚类模型选择最优聚类簇数目¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.cluster import DBSCAN

for i in np.arange(10.8,12.6,0.2):
    for j in np.arange(2,10):
        DB=DBSCAN(eps=i,min_samples=j).fit(pca_trans)
        labels=DB.labels_
        n_clusters_=len(set(labels))-(1 if -1 in labels else 0)
        n_noise_=labels.tolist().count(-1)
        if n_clusters_ <= 5 and n_noise_ <= 10:
            print("eps={},min_samples={}".format(i,j))
            print("{},{}".format(n_clusters_,n_noise_))
            #print("",labels)
            silh_score=silhouette_score(pca_trans,DB.labels_)
            cali_score=calinski_harabasz_score(pca_trans,DB.labels_)          
            print("silhouette{}".format(silh_score))
            print("calinski_harabasz{}".format(cali_score))
            print("\n---------------------------------------\n")
